    After creating a new frame, you add matrices via:

    ```python

    framew.add_matrix(signature, numpy_array)
    
    ```

    After finishing adding matrices, `.write` must be called:
    
    ```python
    framew.write()
    ```

    Alternatively you can do:

    ```python
